column5: Well, was skunked today. No Pike/Walleye  But going to try again Tomorrow.  How ever the only 2 fish I did catch was a Smally and a Drum  The Bait Box in the photo is 7"x11"  I am pickin up a scale and tape to measure and weigh before I hit the water tomorrow!  Too bad Bass wasn't in season! that would of been a nice dinner! )
Not so good to post out of season fish

Well eaither way, he was back in the water in less then one min...  Didn't even bother wasting time to get my good camera from the car only 20 feet away.. Used my cell to shoot the pic. Considering it was my PB Smally I wasn't giving up a pic before setting him free.
Nicelooking Bass forsure im gettin the itch already!!!
It was released. That's all that matters!
